bda063e2-8f0d-4afc-afce-02cdf3589e26.title: Betty
bda063e2-8f0d-4afc-afce-02cdf3589e26.text:
Well, if you see anyone who is into magic, please send
them my way.

options.text: 遰 Talk to Betty about the Hand in the Sand.
Talk to Betty about her shop.

5d22a1cb-bd65-4ce6-b817-43caefa48cb2.title: Betty
5d22a1cb-bd65-4ce6-b817-43caefa48cb2.text:
I heard from Zavistic what a good job you did. If you
want some more pink dye, I have made up a batch and
you can have some for 20 gold.

59a91668-9821-44f5-aa68-e5dd837944b5.text: You hand over 20 gold pieces in return for the dye

1c7dca7e-abaf-4881-a1d4-f29f42eb51a2.title: <player>
1c7dca7e-abaf-4881-a1d4-f29f42eb51a2.text:
No thanks Betty. Good luck with the shop, I might be
back for some dye later.

ec25d679-0ae0-470e-b55c-33c5e830e6f4.text: You don't have enough money at the moment, come back later.

49e2e17d-257f-4892-97a4-2a80ed025ef8.title: <player>
49e2e17d-257f-4892-97a4-2a80ed025ef8.text:
I've come from Yanille, the wizard says you can make
Truth Serum?

26abd855-1e13-4573-a5cd-8120fb4b5a06.title: Betty
26abd855-1e13-4573-a5cd-8120fb4b5a06.text: This is true deary, I'll need an empty vial.

6776ad5b-03fe-48da-853a-e224df3aa4ee.title: <player>
6776ad5b-03fe-48da-853a-e224df3aa4ee.text: I'll have to go find one then, I'll be back!

07f7f979-58b5-4ab4-8b13-3c637ab38720.title: Betty
07f7f979-58b5-4ab4-8b13-3c637ab38720.text:
That's good, now you'll need to make a rose tinted lens.
Pink dye can be made from red berries in this bottle to
make redberry juice, then add white berries. Just use
that on a bullseye lens.

945ce4c0-edfd-42b4-94c2-00ee0230d250.title: Betty
945ce4c0-edfd-42b4-94c2-00ee0230d250.text: Hello deary! Have you managed to make that lens yet?

8fc19c72-81d9-4c44-86bb-34bc19ba5ec9.title: Betty
8fc19c72-81d9-4c44-86bb-34bc19ba5ec9.text:
Pink dye can be made from red berries in the bottle I
gave you. Add white berries to make the pink dye and
then you just need to use that on a bullseye lens. Good
luck!

18bfe8a7-6568-45de-ae54-f73c0f433b36.title: Betty
18bfe8a7-6568-45de-ae54-f73c0f433b36.text:
Oh don't worry about that deary, I have plenty and
you can start the whole thing again.

430c31a2-854b-4cec-a577-c1da96dd97b1.title: Betty
430c31a2-854b-4cec-a577-c1da96dd97b1.text:
Wonderful deary. When you're ready, just stand in
the open doorway and focus the light on the empty vial
on my desk and I'll pour the serum into it.

2a2c613c-971a-4ff0-9f8a-d987b0deca7d.title: Betty
2a2c613c-971a-4ff0-9f8a-d987b0deca7d.text:
Why it makes the person who drinks it unable to hide
in the shadow of lies. The light of truth will shine!

9abdf628-c029-499b-8b2a-af6bcbb31a7b.text: Betty places a vial on her counter.

1af53b75-b977-414e-b3f5-5379a2f36e23.title: Betty
1af53b75-b977-414e-b3f5-5379a2f36e23.text:
That's not a problem, I kept some of it here just in
case, here you are!

6c83a4bd-92d0-4f42-9a49-fb4dceebc4fe.text: Betty hands you a new vial of truth serum.

cd62c9d4-0390-43bd-bc7d-fc80b425f086.title: Betty
cd62c9d4-0390-43bd-bc7d-fc80b425f086.text:
Ok, now the last ingredient, something personal from the
person you need to tell the truth, else it won't work!

57188144-6872-4512-9565-feb3d47868ad.title: <player>
57188144-6872-4512-9565-feb3d47868ad.text: Ok, I'll see if I can find something.

9d4051a7-fb91-4c3d-a49b-53154ce26bb0.title: Betty
9d4051a7-fb91-4c3d-a49b-53154ce26bb0.text:
Ok, now the last ingredient, something personal from the
person you need to tell the truth, else it won't work!

808ceeb2-5dd1-40a3-92ad-01b751ec8c8f.title: <player>
808ceeb2-5dd1-40a3-92ad-01b751ec8c8f.text: What about this sand straight from his pocket?

be57ed14-0b3f-4ad5-9545-9970ad16bcf1.text:
You hand the sand over and watch Betty sprinkle it in
the serum, it fizzes.

95945ee8-ff92-4df3-8f66-5837d08a7b98.title: Betty
95945ee8-ff92-4df3-8f66-5837d08a7b98.text: Don't forget to dilute it in something like tea or coffee.

6db2e76d-9c68-4cdf-9bab-d416acaa6f09.title: Betty
6db2e76d-9c68-4cdf-9bab-d416acaa6f09.text: Hello deary! How did the serum work?

193c8dc1-1593-4ddd-97a0-dd695717097e.title: Betty
193c8dc1-1593-4ddd-97a0-dd695717097e.text:
Well don't forget to dilute it in a drink or something
else bad things might happen.

18b994d6-f41b-43da-a357-b3f762dcd78f.title: <player>
18b994d6-f41b-43da-a357-b3f762dcd78f.text: Oh! I... see. I'll remember to dilute it then.

options.text: I've forgotten how to use the serum.

17b74ed0-63ab-4223-89dd-791464cef25d.title: <player>
17b74ed0-63ab-4223-89dd-791464cef25d.text: I've forgotten how to use the serum.

16c39284-de93-4cd7-be31-5726285c2fde.title: Betty
16c39284-de93-4cd7-be31-5726285c2fde.text:
It must be diluted in a drink or something else bad
things might happen.

e8a55fb7-d8e8-4071-8267-3167ebe460f4.title: Betty
e8a55fb7-d8e8-4071-8267-3167ebe460f4.text:
That's not a problem, I kept some of it here just in
case, here you are!

b78821c6-2461-4ed2-9c65-7e4d3e3697f6.text: Betty hands you a new vial of truth serum.

919c8740-e3bd-4ae5-9ecb-8c487552a6fd.title: Betty
919c8740-e3bd-4ae5-9ecb-8c487552a6fd.text:
Hello again deary. Come back and tell me what
happened when all the fuss is over.

6dd5fb84-5694-487b-b28f-9e2c77cde2a6.title: Betty
6dd5fb84-5694-487b-b28f-9e2c77cde2a6.text:
I heard from Zavistic what a good job you did. If you
want some more pink dye, I have made up a batch and
you can have some for 20 gold.

1d9481fe-11e3-4c5a-b251-f3419eaf51e9.text: You hand over 20 gold pieces in return for the dye

7b82301a-d816-457d-b1fa-ebcc7e7b677c.title: <player>
7b82301a-d816-457d-b1fa-ebcc7e7b677c.text:
No thanks Betty. Good luck with the shop, I might be
back for some dye later.
